WEBVTT

00:00.651 --> 00:12.039
Use "has" for he, she and it. Use "have" for I, you, we, they, don't and doesn't.

00:14.473 --> 00:16.941
I have a nice bicycle.

00:20.745 --> 00:23.123
I don't have a sports car.

00:26.927 --> 00:31.867
You have a blue shirt while I have a white shirt.

00:35.760 --> 00:37.507
Trump has blond hair.

00:41.226 --> 00:44.035
He doesn't have long hair.

00:47.647 --> 00:50.460
She doesn't have a boyfriend.

00:54.018 --> 00:57.034
The dog has very short legs.

00:58.006 --> 01:00.697
It doesn't have a long tail.

01:04.465 --> 01:06.623
We have a big family.

01:10.471 --> 01:12.629
They have brown hair.

